{"tid":2496149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲男末日! 中情局預測 日港澳坡韓台全球最低生育率 連登最憎既Niger奪最高生育率","createTime":"2021-04-19T15:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T15:24:19.000Z","uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82b914c9c20304be6e1443942b008b2ae4c9d8c8","tid":2496149,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"原link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/field/total-fertility-rate/country-comparison\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Fthe-world-factbook%2Ffield%2Ftotal-fertility-rate%2Fcountry-comparison&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuDrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=22285d77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/field/total-fertility-rate/country-comparison</a><br />\n蘋果:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210418/YFJTZ5I5BZEINIXW45UDW6MSDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210418%2FYFJTZ5I5BZEINIXW45UDW6MSDU%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuDrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=ff91eb87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210418%2FYFJTZ5I5BZEINIXW45UDW6MSDU%2F&h=2694cf35\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210418/YFJTZ5I5BZEINIXW45UDW6MSDU/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國中情局（CIA）公布2021全年全球人口生育率預測，墊底的五個國家都在亞洲，分別是香港、澳門、新加坡、南韓，而台灣居末。<br />\n<br />\n根據Big News Network網站17日報導，中情局預測全球227個國家或地區生育率，數據指出，每名15至45歲台灣女性，只會擁有1.07個孩子。報導指出，生育率會直接影響國家經濟狀態，也是判斷人口健康與教育程度的重要元素。<br />\n<br />\n在227個國家或地區中，非洲國家包辦前13名。生育率低的國家最後5名由亞洲國家包辦，台灣生育率世界最低。<br />\n218 日本1.38 <br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n223 香港 1.22 <br />\n224 澳門 1.21 <br />\n225 玻國 1.15 <br />\n226 南韓 1.09 <br />\n227 台灣 1.07<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/taCa8Wp4CDNRKqbc58vttbOoU2c=/760x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5M74VS3UX5HDXKCXHCKPAZVZY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtaCa8Wp4CDNRKqbc58vttbOoU2c%3D%2F760x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5M74VS3UX5HDXKCXHCKPAZVZY4.jpg&h=cd566207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報導引述台灣內政部數據稱，台灣去年只有16萬5249個新生嬰兒，創下歷史新低，也是首次死亡人數超過出生人數。而今年第一季新生兒出生人數僅3萬4917人，同比減少13.6%，數字再度探低。<br />\n<br />\n專家指出，如果出生率持續下降，可能會阻礙經濟增長，且對社會保障網絡將會是一項挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n報告稱，在已開發國家生育率普遍較低，因為當地民眾對於生育控制已有概念。而在台灣，許多女性必須外出白天工作，晚上回家還需要操持家務及照顧兒童，這也是低生育率的原因之一。（余浚安／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYmLx6YBNyLoqwiJLiuKSPh1FKw51Rmc7BDpfbupvFPYU?filename=ig9uJPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fig9uJPY.jpg&h=b3e3d461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東亞人滅絕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e73932fb93deea99859a5bb6d46eba353bdeabc","tid":2496149,"uid":344824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:23:45.000Z","msg":"冇計蠢人永遠多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a410310e370bcb9a2ca2bbb23e63280aa087095","tid":2496149,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"其實歐洲生育率都係好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一旦城市化之後都會生少咗人。<br />\n<br />\n越窮嘅地方就會生得越多，呢點喺5, 60年代嘅支那已經反映曬，多到要後來搞一孩政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將來呢個世界分分鐘得返黑人同埋中東蛔佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c765605e51465fda462dbfe1dca29495c6bd23","tid":2496149,"uid":344824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T15:24:19.000Z","msg":"Matt__Leung仲未入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}